snippet.title: Ynglet Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A game made by Nifflas and Hotdog with help from Triple Topping;

Swim and bounce through this meditative floating platformer. My own dynamically generated music sets the soundscape for your exploration through Ynglet’s hand-drawn levels.

You can follow Nifflas creating Ynglet here: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Nifflas
STEAM: http://bit.ly/3cmtHs4
Itch.io: bit.ly/3abUMv7
Discord: bit.ly/3acmBng
